Created attachment 1176 src.opensolaris.org page with multiple project descriptions
src.opensolaris.org currently has number of projects. Some of the projects have a description of the internal structure just below the search menu (see the attached screenshots).
This does not scale with number of projects. With that big number of unrelated projects it does not make much sense to have a detailed description of all the projects on the front page.
Instead, it should be possible for each project to have its own description which could be dynamically displayed under the search fields (by clicking on the project name, for instance).
Also, from usability perspective, everything should fit on single page.

attachment.desc: src.opensolaris.org page with multiple project descriptions
